{"tid":2198178,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"還押七個月 18 歲音樂導師認向葵涌警署擲汽油彈 月底判刑","createTime":"2020-09-11T07:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T10:13:31.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"babeb465e30f9799fb54f00ef3a294fa4ce8b78b","tid":2198178,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:16:26.000Z","msg":"今年 1 月葵涌警署懷疑被 3 名黑衣人投擲汽油彈，事後一名 18 歲音樂導師被起訴，指他涉嫌在警署車閘位置縱火。案件今（11日）在區域法院聽取答辯，被告承認一項企圖縱火及一項管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產。辯方求情指被告患有過度活躍症，希望法官判刑時考慮被告此病，法官胡雅文將案件押後至 9 月 28 日，以索取精神科醫生報告及教導所報告，期間被告須繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E4%B8%83%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-18-%E6%AD%B2%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E5%B0%8E%E5%B8%AB%E8%AA%8D%E5%90%91%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E6%93%B2%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E4%25B8%2583%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-18-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25B0%258E%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%2593%25B2%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fqQBVxexyTzYM5wEVuQb9nQ%3D&h=32fe1a0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E4%25B8%2583%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-18-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25B0%258E%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%2593%25B2%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591%2F&h=c4cb8fc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E4%B8%83%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-18-%E6%AD%B2%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E5%B0%8E%E5%B8%AB%E8%AA%8D%E5%90%91%E8%91